thread.title: KV

author: KV
title: KV
text:
Been shopping here for years, cheap and reliable.
Just bought Battlefield 1. It did take 5 hours to deliver the key to my inbox, but usually the delivery is fairly automatic, and will be delivered within a few minutes. Never had any issues with invalid keys, or no deliveries.
If you are looking to buy a new game, and you are checking for cheap prices on various websites, include CDKH in your search!
